    <item>
      <title>保罗·都铎·琼斯对新世界大战的恐惧影响了政策制定者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2023-12-01/hedge-fund-managers-consider-world-war-a-growing-possibility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[相互关联的冲突的扩散引发了人们与过去的世界大战的比较——并使政策制定者集中精力采取措施防止冲突升级]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2023-12-01/hedge-fund-managers-consider-world-war-a-growing-possibility</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 05:00:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德桑蒂斯和纽瑟姆在集会基地对峙，目光聚焦白宫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-01/desantis-newsom-rally-bases-in-debate-with-eyes-toward-future</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佛罗里达州州长罗恩·德桑蒂斯 (Ron DeSantis) 和加利福尼亚州州长加文·纽瑟姆 (Gavin Newsom) 在税收、边境安全和能源等问题上展开了一场辩论，这场辩论是 2024 年总统竞选的一场余兴节目——也许还能瞥见下一个。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-01/desantis-newsom-rally-bases-in-debate-with-eyes-toward-future</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 04:14:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克花费 16 亿英镑试图向 COP 表明他正在传达信息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/sunak-pledges-1-6-billion-to-try-to-show-cop28-he-s-on-message</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 在淡化政府的绿色议程并承诺提振石油产量后，在出席 COP28 峰会时承诺将斥资 16 亿英镑（20 亿美元）用于气候项目，试图向领导人表明英国仍然致力于这一事业和天然气勘探。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/sunak-pledges-1-6-billion-to-try-to-show-cop28-he-s-on-message</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>顾问称，米雷领导下的阿根廷不会加入金砖国家集团</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/argentina-won-t-join-the-brics-bloc-under-milei-adviser-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即将上任的高级外交官表示，在哈维尔·米雷担任总统期间，阿根廷不会加入中国领导的金砖国家集团，这突显了他的政府计划在上任后发生的重大外交政策转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/argentina-won-t-join-the-brics-bloc-under-milei-adviser-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 18:38:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共同社称香港记者北京之行后失踪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/south-china-morning-post-reporter-missing-after-beijing-trip-kyodo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据共同社周四报道，自 10 月份前往北京报道防务论坛以来，香港主要英文报纸的一名记者一直无法联系上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/south-china-morning-post-reporter-missing-after-beijing-trip-kyodo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 16:43:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
